evolve, with new tools and techniques emerging regularly. Staying current with these changes is essential for any web developer.</p>\n    \n    <p>By understanding the core principles and keeping up with industry trends, developers can build better, faster, and more maintainable web applications.</p>\n  0:{\"rsc\":[\"$\",\"$1\",\"c\",{\"children\":[[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"className\":\"container mx-auto px-4 py-8\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"h1\",null,{\"className\":\"text-3xl font-bold mb-6\",\"children\":\"Ad Inserter Demo\"}],[\"$\",\"p\",null,{\"className\":\"text-gray-600 mb-8\",\"children\":\"This page demonstrates the ad inserter system for Google AdSense and other ad networks. Ads can be inserted anywhere on the site or within content.\"}],[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"className\":\"grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-8\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"className\":\"lg:col-span-2\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"className\":\"bg-white rounded-lg shadow p-6 mb-8\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"h2\",null,{\"className\":\"text-xl font-semibold mb-4\",\"children\":\"Content with Automatic Ad Insertion\"}],[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"className\":\"prose max-w-none\",\"children\":[\"$\",\"$L2\",null,{\"content\":\"$3\",\"adFrequency\":2,\"className\":\"mt-4\"}]}]]}],[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"className\":\"bg-white rounded-lg shadow p-6\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"h2\",null,{\"className\":\"text-xl font-semibold mb-4\",\"children\":\"Individual Ad Placements\"}],[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"className\":\"space-y-6\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"children\":[[\"$\",\"h3\",null,{\"className\":\"font-medium mb-2\",\"children\":\"Header Ad\"}],[\"$\",\"$L4\",null,{\"placement\":\"header\",\"className\":\"border border-gray-200 rounded p-4\"}]]}],[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"children\":[[\"$\",\"h3\",null,{\"className\":\"font-medium mb-2\",\"children\":\"Sidebar Ad\"}],[\"$\",\"$L4\",null,{\"placement\":\"sidebar\",\"className\":\"border border-gray-200 rounded p-4\"}]]}],[\"$\",\"div\",null